 on-shell\nextrapolation. We comment on the prospects for neutron structure extraction in\ntagged DIS with EIC. We discuss possible extensions of the FSI model to other\nkinematic regions (large/small x). In tagged DIS at x << 0.1 FSI resulting from\ndiffractive scattering on the nucleons become important and require separate\ntreatment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2017 16:28:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-04"}
