city of 0.04 $\\pm$ 0.02, matching other systems\nwith similar periods. Furthermore, a correlation between accreted mass and\norbital period was found, as well as a possible relation between the initial\nmass-ratio and the final period-eccentricity. The wide sdB-binary sample shows\ninteresting possible correlations between orbital and spectral properties.\nHowever, a larger sample is necessary to statistically validate them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2017 17:59:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-20"}
