ta$ or $\\sigma_\\phi$\nand $\\beta \\simeq 0.5$. The apparent metallicity contrariety in the rotation\nvelocity among the halo sub-populations supports the co-existence of multiple\npopulations in the galactic halo that may have formed through distinct\nformation scenarios, i.e. in-situ versus accretion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2017 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-26"}
