ple wallets to gain more than 4.5M USD from mid-July to\nmid-August 2017. Our findings should prompt the Ripple community to improve the\nhealth of the network by educating its users on increasing their connectivity,\nand by appropriately maintaining the credit limits, rippling flags, and\nexchange offers on their credit links.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2017 19:42:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Mar 2018 22:44:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-13"}
