 a\npercentage of fully 3D Fourier modes in the volume.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2017 20:28:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Nov 2017 23:38:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-23"}
